The quick brown fox

## Development setup

Install required Python dependencies before running the test suite or
launching the referendum simulator:

```
pip install -r requirements-dev.txt
```

The tests that exercise the referendum workflow require `pandas` and
`numpy`. Pytest will skip those suites automatically if the modules are
missing, but installing the dependencies is recommended for full
coverage.

## Referendum simulator

The referendum simulator projects referendum outcomes using dated party
endorsements, election baselines, and the trained referendum model. For
detailed CLI and web usage instructions see
[`docs/referendum_simulator.md`](docs/referendum_simulator.md).
